## âš ï¸ Known Limitations

### Touch Pressure
- Only works on devices with pressure sensors
- iOS: 3D Touch (iPhone 6S - iPhone XS)
- Android: Some devices support pressure estimation
- Falls back to 0 if unavailable

### Device Motion
- Requires user permission on iOS 13+
- May not work in all browsers
- Falls back gracefully if unavailable

### Device Model Detection
- Best-effort user agent parsing
- May show "Unknown" for some devices
- Screen dimensions always captured

